    "image_with_content_EGjCcT": {
      "type": "image-with-content",
      "name": "Image + Content (Combat)",
      "settings": {
        "image_position": "right",
        "kicker": "",
        "heading": "OUR STORY",
        "richtext": "<p>Elite Ti started in a garage with one goal: build parts we’d trust on our own cars. That same mindset scaled into a global carbon fiber and titanium brand for JDM and time attack builds. Everything we make follows the same rule. Make it lighter. Make it stronger. Make it perfect.</p><p><strong>WHAT DRIVES US</strong></p><p>We don’t chase shortcuts. We chase fitment, finish, and performance that actually delivers. Every weave, curve, and bracket is built with intent, tested on real cars, and refined until it looks right and works right.</p><p><strong>MISSION</strong></p><p>Create high quality parts with precision craftsmanship and give every customer a smooth experience from the first message to final install.</p><p><strong>VISION</strong></p><p>Lead the custom composite world by staying focused on innovation, precision, and individuality. We don’t follow trends. We build our own lane.</p>",
        "button_label": "Read the full story",
        "button_link": "shopify://pages/about_us",
        "content_bg": "#0f1315",
        "text_color": "#ffffff",
        "button_bg": "#a7ff1e",
        "button_text_color": "#111111",
        "content_max": 820,
        "desktop_min_height": 600,
        "pad_top": 0,
        "pad_bottom": 0
      }
    },
